    <h1>Centroid Bias</h1>
    <p class="description">Google's tendency to rank businesses closer to a city's <strong>geographic center</strong> higher in local pack results — especially for broad "in [city]" queries. Reduced by the 2021 Vicinity Update but never fully eliminated.</p>
