              <tr><td><strong>"dentist Round Rock"</strong> (suburb)</td><td>Suburb centroid</td><td class="cell-yes">Low — you're the local</td><td>Neighborhood landing pages</td></tr>
              <tr><td><strong>"dentist 78704"</strong> (ZIP)</td><td>ZIP centroid</td><td class="cell-yes">Low</td><td>Location match + prominence</td></tr>
            </tbody>
